text: François Eisenbarth (27 March 1928 - 17 September 1987) was a Luxembourgian gymnast. He competed in six events at the 1960 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1928 births Category:1987 deaths Category:Luxembourgian male artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of Luxembourg Category:Gymnasts at the 1960 Summer Olympics Category:People from Rumelange
